claim.claim-text:
1. A process for tracking skilled-service rendered a patient by a provider at a treatment location, comprising the steps of: 
generating, at the treatment location, at least one record of progress made toward each treatment goal identified for the patient and addressed by the provider during a treatment session; 
receiving an input comprising each said record of progress so generated, for storage as treatment record data at a host location; 
using said treatment record data and a host processor, automatically generating a patient report; and 
submitting said patient report to an entity selected from the group consisting of a health care facility, a health care provider, an insurer, the patient, an entity authorized to receive records of the patient, and a record-keeping entity for the provider.
